snippet.title: PureSocial Network
snippet.description:
Welcome to PureSocial™
PureSocial Network is a social media movement giving control of rating the news into the hands of the people. Where you have control over the conversation and everyone is a journalist. Your voice will be heard through the power of “the vote” with our "Crowdscore™ Rating system" - creating press accountability and offering diversity of thought. 

We are a non-traditional smart media platform that was developed outside of the Silicon Valley bubble. We exist to provide real, unbiased, trusted news. Our policy is that everyone has a voice… those on the right, the left, and everyone in-between. 

PureSocialTV™ is a brand new video network with uncensored videos currently being removed from big tech. If you support free speech and you want to learn from other human beings vs. machine learning, check it out at https://www.puresocial.tv

PureSocial™ - Join the conversation!
